de.ityx.mediatrix.api.client

Interface ICServiceCenter


  • public interface ICServiceCenter
    Provides functions to manage the global parameter for the client ServiceCenter.
    How to use:
    API.getClientAPI().getServiceCenterAPI().refresh(servicecenter);
